1-1-1 Peanut butter cookies

Ingredients:

1 egg
1 cup (2.4 dl) sugar
1 cup (2.4 dl) peanut butter


Preparation:

Preheat the oven to 190 C (375 F).  Mix the egg with the sugar.  Blend
in the peanut butter.  Form walnut-sized balls with a spoon and put on
a "plåt".  Flatten the balls with a fork.  Bake for about 10 minutes.
